                     <interp inst="t18450818-1592-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> stealing, on the <rs id="t18450818-cd-7" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450818-1592-offence-1 t18450818-cd-7"></join>2nd of Aug.</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18450818-name-127" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-127" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-127" type="surname" value="KIRBY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-127" type="given" value="JOHN JOHNSON"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450818-1592-offence-1 t18450818-name-127"></join>John Johnson Kirby</persName>, from his person; to which</rs>
